==English==

===Adjective===
'''mercenary'''
# One who is motived by private gain.

See [[greedy]], [[venal]]

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''mercenary'''
# A person who is employed to [[fight]] in an armed conflict, whose [[prime]] or [[sole]] motivation is that of private gain and not a member of the [[state]] or [[military]] group that they are fighting for.

Compare [[soldier]].

